body:
The following syntax defines the `autoEmbed` type:

```javascript
{
  "fields": [
    {
      "type": "autoEmbed",
      "modality": "text",
      "path": "<field-name>",
      "model": "<embedding-model>"
    },
    {
      "type": "filter",
      "path": "<field-to-index>"
    },
    ...
  ]
}
```
